- Configuration Reloading: Integrated dynamic hot-reloading configurations in `cmd/serve.go` and `cmd/config.go` on receiving `SIGHUP` signals.
- Config CLI Commands: Re-introduced and polished missing commands `mls config open` and `mls config reveal`.
